title: In These Words Chapters 10-13 & Side Stories
description:
A collection of Guilt|Pleasure works.

Contains chapters 10, 11, 12, 13, Wrapped Around Your Finger, The Bride, Undertow, the sample of The Doll, and the clean English scans of First Do No Harm.

The sample of The Doll is a .pdf file

Everything else is a .rar of a folder of .png or .jpg images.

Unfortunately, chapters 12 and 13 are not clean scans, but the pictures are legible and are the only source currently available
